nt\r\n	<ol>\r\n		<li>Explain the difference between the different plans</li>\r\n	</ol>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n',1,1,'2016-08-23 14:52:46','2016-08-23 14:52:46',NULL),(89,44,24,'Setting Up 1Password','Instructions for how to set up 1Password ','<p>At Mayden we use 1Password to store both personal and company authentication details in a secure and easily accessible way. 1Password will give you access to both a personal vault and also&nbsp;a Mayden team vault, which will enable you access to login details for things like the Demo iaptus site, databases and company ecommerce accounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Follow these steps to get set up:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Sign Up for a 1Password Account</li>\r\n	<li>Download and Set Up 1Password Desktop App</li>\r\n	<li>Request a Mayden Team Vault invite from a member of the SysOps team</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Signing Up for a 1Password Account</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To sign up for a 1Password account, go <a href=\"https://start.1password.com/signup/team?type=I\">here</a>&nbsp;and enter your Mayden email address.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Follow the sign up dialogs, opting for a personal account when prompted, and making a note of your 1Password key</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Downloading and Setting Up 1Password Desktop App</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Download and install the software for your operating system <a href=\"https://agilebits.com/downloads\">here</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Open the program and log in using the details you got from step 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Request a Mayden Team Vault Invite</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ask a member of the SysOps team to send you an email invite to the Mayden Vault. The current designated 1Password Guru is Matt E.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Follow the instructions in the email invite and follow the dialogs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n',1,1,'2016-08-23 14:53:13','2016-08-23 14:53:13',NULL),(90,44,24,'Setting Up 1Password','Instructions for how to set up 1Password ','<p>At Mayden we use 1Password to store both personal and company authentication details in a secure and easily accessible way. 1Password will give you access to both a personal vault and also&nbsp;a Mayden team vault, which will enable you access to login details for things like the Demo iaptus site, databases and company ecommerce accounts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Follow these steps to get set up:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Sign Up for a 1Password Account</li>\r\n	<li>Download and Set Up 1Password Desktop App</li>\r\n	<li>Request a Mayden Team Vault invite from a member of the SysOps team</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. Signing Up for a 1Password Account</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To sign up for a 1Password account, go <a href=\"https://start.1password.com/signup/team?type=I\">here</a>&nbsp;and enter your Mayden email address.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Follow the sign up dialogs, opting for a personal account when prompted, and making a note of your 1Password key</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Downloading and Setting Up 1Password Desktop App</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Download and install the software for your operating system <a href=\"https://agilebits.com/downloads\">here</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Open the program and log in using the details you got from step 1</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Request a Mayden Team Vault Invite</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ask a member of the SysOps team to send you an email invite to the Mayden Vault. The current designated 1Password Guru is Matt E.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Follow the instructions in the email invite and follow the dialogs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Notes</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Maintain a distinction between your personal vault and the Mayden vault or you&#39;ll end up sharing your private details with the whole company!</p>\r\n',1,1,'2016-08-23 14:55:08','2016-08-23 14:55:08',NULL),(91,32,23,'New Developer Setup','A few things to cover when getting a new starter set up in an iaptus team.','<h3>Core Mayden Tools